Description: Here is an extremely nice 2017 Fender Road Worn Stratocaster in Olympic White.... I purchased this guitar because of it's playability.... Smooth fast "C" shape neck that feels worn in.... Super low action with NO BUZZ.... Awesome feel and Sweet Vintage Vibe!To be honest, I was going to load in some Crazy Hot Pickups and have this as a Monster Strat, I just couldn't do it. The guitar sounds and plays too go to molest it like that. It is a 100% stock Fender Stratocaster Tone to the Bone.
